■ When you use the default value of the optimize_constant_feedback_seqs
attribute, the following netlist is written after mapping:
module test(clk, a, z, z2);
input clk, a;
output z, z2;
wire clk, a;
wire z, z2;
assign z2 = 1'b1;
assign z = 1'b0;
